Review.create(rating: 5, comment: "Breath of the Wild is Nintendo's most impressive and ambitious game to date", game: zelda)
Review.create(rating: 5, comment: "I... have never been so taken aback by the vastness of a game. You really don't need to read another review, Zelda alone is worth the price of a switch. Like if they sold this game for 300 dollars I would probably buy it. In fact, it's the only Switch game I own, and have no real plans to purchase anything else because between the original game and Master Mode, I will be getting a divorce soon so I can spend more time collecting mushrooms and climbing mountains.", game: zelda)
